FT  25 MAR 92 / Boost for R&amp;D is urged
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
THE Semiconductor Manufacturers Association said yesterday that whoever won
the election needed to understand the importance of encouraging industry to
invest in training and research and development.
Mr Ken Sanders, managing director of Texas Instruments, the US semiconductor
